        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <p>At Shoe Shop, we are committed to protecting and securing our customers' personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you access our website.</p>
        
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you visit our website and make a purchase, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Shipping address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Payment information (if applicable)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your personal information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To process orders and deliver products.</li>
            <li>To communicate with you regarding your order or provide customer support.</li>
            <li>To improve the website and user experience.</li>
            <li>To send promotional notifications and information about new products (if you agree).</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>3. Protecting Your Personal Information</h2>
        <p>We are committed to protecting your personal information through appropriate security measures. However, you should also be cautious when providing information over the Internet, as no data transmission method is completely secure.</p>
        
        <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to request corrections, updates, or deletions of your personal information by contacting us via email or our customer support phone number.</p>
        
        <h2>5. Sharing Information with Third Parties</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with any third parties unless necessary to provide our services (e.g., shipping, payment) or as required by law.</p>
        
        <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies to track customer behavior and improve our services. You can disable cookies through your browser settings if you do not wish to use this feature.</p>
        
        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us via email at support@shopgiay.com or call us at (012) 3456 789.</p>
        
        <h2>8. Policy Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be announced on our website, and the updated version will take effect as soon as it is posted.</p>
        
